title: Intel’s Raptor Lake refresh prices have leaked, and hikes are on the way
description: Intel's upcoming Raptor Lake refresh is just around the corner, and this new price leak tells us that buyers will have a difficult choice ahead.

title: Trump’s lawyer brought a gaming laptop to $250M fraud trial
description: Of all the places we'd expect to see a gaming laptop, President Trump's fraud trial was definitely not one of them.

title: iPhone 15 Pro overheating? Apple is (finally) on the case
description: It took more than two weeks, but Apple has finally responded to the overheating issue affecting the new iPhone 15 Pro and iPhone 15 Pro Max.

title: Apple is done with the $17,000 gold Apple Watch Edition
description: Apple will no longer fix or offer any other kind of service for the first-generation of Apple Watches, including the 18-karat gold Apple Watch Edition.

title: Tom Hanks warns of AI-generated ad using his likeness
description: Tom Hanks has warned his fans not to be fooled by an AI-generated ad circulating online that appears to show him endorsing a dental plan.
